title: Don't Think Twice
actors: Mike Birbiglia, Gillian Jacobs, Kate Micucci, Tami Sagher
plot: JACK (Keegan Michael Key) & his girlfriend Samantha (Gillian Jacobs) are a perfect couple who are also Teammates on a popular improv group that perform at a struggling comedy spot in NYC. Together, the team has a family like bond but individually they have their personal dreams of being on the weekly television show "This Weekend Live".
